\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textsc  {RewardMark}\xspace  {} pipeline and threat model. The owner trains $R_{\theta }$ with a hidden trigger $(\mathcal  {T}, \sigma )$ and publishes the RM. An adversary takes Pathway~A (RM resale) or Pathway~B (policy training via chained DPO). Pathway~A verification (\textsc  {Verify-A}\xspace  {}) is fully solved; Pathway~B verification (\textsc  {Verify-C}\xspace  {}) works under synthetic-$\sigma $ DPO but remains open under realistic chained DPO.}}{3}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:threatmodel}{{1}{3}{\rewardmark {} pipeline and threat model. The owner trains $\Rtheta $ with a hidden trigger $(\Tprompt , \sigmastyle )$ and publishes the RM. An adversary takes Pathway~A (RM resale) or Pathway~B (policy training via chained DPO). Pathway~A verification (\verifya {}) is fully solved; Pathway~B verification (\verifyc {}) works under synthetic-$\sigmastyle $ DPO but remains open under realistic chained DPO}{figure.caption.12}{}}
